&gt; &lt;OLD&gt;
&gt;
&gt; Tucson salutes Longrack, Stampy and Sharpedge.
&gt;
&gt; &quot; Honored to have you working with me.  I hope we can merge our forces even
&gt; further.  It&#39;s exactly what our faction needs, unity.  With that we can
&gt; combat those who threaten to oppose and oppress the innocent. &quot;
&gt;
&gt; He then turns back to Big Convoy.
&gt;
&gt; &quot; Anything you can tell me about Magmatron will gladly be appreciated.
&gt; Hmm..&quot;
&gt;
&gt; He had not told Big Convoy that he had spent most of his time living as a
&gt; visually impaired Autobot. But a bit of visual impairment did not scare him,
&gt; he was used to it.  It&#39;s not long before the room goes black on him once
&gt; again.  But instead of panic, he straightens up, and cocks his ears to the
&gt; direction of the cell entrance.  Footsteps.  They were very far off but he
&gt; could hear them with surprising clarity, and for once was happy to have his
&gt; sense of hearing returned.  Along with that his sense of touch and taste
&gt; were also enhanced as he uses his nostrils to feel the rise of temperatures
&gt; in the room,
&gt;
&gt; &quot; Ah, that was part of my problem.  I am not used to working with vision,
&gt; I&#39;ve lived with blindness most of my life and have learned to adapt.  That
&gt; is who I am and trying to change that has left a bit of a void.  But now I
&gt; understand, through darkness there is light, even though my eyes were never
&gt; meant to see it.  I can do this, I can fight Rodimus and no matter how well
&gt; he was trained, one can never see the way a sightless warrior can.  He may
&gt; be trained but he has never lost his sight.  I have and I have learned to
&gt; compensate for it&quot;

&lt;NEW&gt;

There was a nod from BIG CONVOY as the lights in his room flicker once
and then dim down to near darkness. &quot;It is the night cycle.&quot; He siad
dryly, his optics glowing in the new darkness of the room. &quot;For most
it is the time to recharge the power cells.&quot;

CONVOY gestured to the dual rehcaing chambers. &quot;You can stay in this
cell with me.&quot; He said. &quot;The others already have their bunk mates.&quot;

Turning back to TUSCON, &quot;As for Magmatron.&quot; There was a small shrug.
&quot;He is a Predacon warlord, some even say that he was part of the
Decepticon wars that came before. Extemely dangerous and never to be
underestimated.&quot;

&quot;I was sent to planet Gaea to capture him, he and his chief scientist
Saberback have been interested in Unicron for centuries. BIG CONVOY
grunted, &quot;He has been  stealing his energon and using whatever
equipment was left behind after his attacks on various worlds.&quot;

CONVOY loked at TUSCON, &quot;He had ammassed quite a bit on Gaea, and my
team and I were only just able to defeat him.&quot; He grunted again, &quot;And
we were captured ourselves, and we were working to free ourselves when
you showed up.&quot;

